data-triple-N3.o: "Harp Lager, (sometimes marketed as Harp Irish Lager) is a Vienna-style lager brand created in 1960 by the Guinness Brewery in its Dundalk brewery. It is a leading lager brand in Ireland, and is also popular in Australia, Canada, Africa and the United States. The product is brewed in the Dundalk brewery in Ireland and the Hydes brewery in Great Britain. In Great Britain distribution is handled by Bargain Beer Supplies."@en
